steps.name: Click on the 'Companies' button from the sidebar menu
Enter the name of the company into the 'Client name' field
Click on the 'Lifecycle stage' dropdown field
Enter Url of the company website into the 'Website URL' field
Enter some name into the 'Search' field the 'Primary Contact' dropdown field
Click on the '+Create new Contact' link from the 'Primary Contact' dropdown
Enter the first name of the primary contact
Enter the last name of the primary contact
Enter the email address of the primary contact
Click on the 'Create' button to create the primary contact user
The success message that the new Company was creates
